name: Limited Edition Custom Designed YOGA MATS
description:
Add ::Wings:: to your yoga practice with these custom designed Yoga Mats!

Limited Edition: Only 7 available of each design! They are going fast!

The First 10 customers to order will receive a FREE Shipibo headband ($20 total value, Now free with your mat purchase!)

All mats measures 72" x 24" with a depth of 1/4" (5mm). With an embossed turmeric colored under side that provides a slip resistant tread. The topside displays an edge-to-edge full color print of the design of your choice. The mat weighs approximately 7lbs and is made from non-allergenic, non-latex closed cell foam construction which prevents absorption of sweat and microbes, and is certified safe for contact with infants. This mat is best suited for DRY YOGA where your hands and feet are sweat free.

Check out also the new HOT YOGA TRAVEL MAT/YOGA TOWEL

Select your model from the 6 designs available in the picture.
More designs coming soon!

name: Limited Edition Custom Designed TRAVEL MAT/YOGA TOWEL
description:
The Perfect compliment for the ::Wings:: Yoga Mats

Limited Edition: Only 7 available of each design! They are going fast!

The First 10 customers to order will receive a FREE Shipibo Headband (A $25 value item, now free with your Yoga Towel purchase!*) 

The TRAVEL MAT/YOGA TOWEL measures 72” x 24” with the thickness of a regular towel. The recycled Natural Rubber reverse is embossed with a high traction grip, while the topside is made from white Polyester Micro-fibre. The mat only weighs 1.5lbs and is a very handy travel companion packing down to only 9” x 5” x 1”. 
The mat also makes a great ‘topper’ to your existing mat or a borrowed mat. This mat is well suited to HOT YOGA


*offer valid while supplies last.

(A percentage of every sale goes to GLOBAL GREEN)
